Package org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.timelineservice.documentstore.lib Description

Package org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.timelineservice. documentstore.lib contains factory class for instantiating different DocumentStore reader writer client based on the DocumentVendor configured.
